==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outstare
<hw>Out*stare"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To excel or
overcome in staring; to face down.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I would <qex>outstare</qex> the sternest eyes that look.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outstart</ent>⟦br⟧
